dc_description_s: This data layer represents hydrography for Ashland County, Wisconsin in 2012. It is a feature class within the geodatabase, Ashland_Hydro_2012.gdb. The feature layers included in the geodatabase are 'Ashland_HydroLine_2012' and 'Ashland_HydroPoly_2012'.
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of data held at UW-Madison. For the most recent version of this data, please visit: https://data-ashlandcountywi.opendata.arcgis.com/
